title: Newborn baby girl, umbilical cord still attached, dies alone in metal trash drum sucking her thumb for comfort. WHO LEFT HER HER TO DIE?
itunes:title: Newborn baby girl, umbilical cord still attached, dies alone in metal trash drum sucking her thumb for comfort. WHO LEFT HER HER TO DIE?
description:
Body of an infant baby girl will be exhumed in hopes of solving her murder. Nancy Grace talks with a panel of experts involved in the case of Baby Jane Doe. Our panel includes: Ashley Wilcott,  Judge and trial attorney; Joseph Scott Morgan, Forensic Expert: Dr. Michelle Dupre, Medical Examiner; Shera LaPoint, Genetic Genealogist; Major Wendell Raborn,  Iberia Parish Sheriff's office; Catalean Theriot, Comprehensive Victim Intervention Specialist Louisiana 16th Judicial District Attorney's Office; and Dave Mack Crime Online Reporter.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
